<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>탈퇴 완료</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 40px; background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; }
        .box { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h2 { color: #e53e3e; }
        .btn-group { margin-top: 30px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0 10px; }
        .btn-home { background-color: #718096; color: white; }
        .btn-rejoin { background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="box">
    <h2>회원 탈퇴가 완료되었습니다</h2>
    <p>그동안 저희 쇼핑몰을 이용해 주셔서 진심으로 감사드립니다.</p>
    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">회원님의 데이터(ID: <strong><%= username %></strong>)는 즉시 안전하게 파기되었습니다.</p>

    <div class="btn-group">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-home">메인 화면으로</a>
        <a href="/user/register" class="btn btn-rejoin">재가입</a>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>